io.github.prolobjectlink.db

Interface Renamer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRenamer, PrologRenamer

    public interface Renamer
    Attribute renamer to prevent variable clashes in prolog queries. Basically convert a class field name in one qualified prolog variable name. The qualified prolog variable name respect the prolog variable syntax. Have methods for convert from Field to PrologVariable and vice-versa. E.g from org.logicware.domain.geometry.Point.idp to ORG_LOGICWARE_DOMAIN_GEOMETRY_POINT_idp_0 from ORG_LOGICWARE_DOMAIN_GEOMETRY_POINT_idp_0 to org.logicware.domain.geometry.Point.idp
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jose Zalacain
    See Also:
    toField(PrologVariable), toVariable(Field)
